project_descr: UNDP Turkey will prepare the NHDR report, the topic of ‘inclusive growth’. Focusing on Turkey’s progress and remaining challenges, this report will look into Turkey’s growth process and dynamics as well as the distribution of growth.

outputs.output_descr: Inclusive programmes for creating jobs and productive livelihoods and improving employability with focus on women, rural and the urban poor and youth that complement sectoral strategies, in place
